data.description: Come tour this two-story dream home in the highly desirable Walden Park Community! This luxurious residence is situated in an exceptional Swim/Tennis Community and boasts a meticulously maintained interior with an open and flowing floor plan that's perfect for entertaining guests. As you step inside, you will fall in love with the grand two-story foyer entrance with a custom iron staircase and gleaming hardwood flooring throughout that leads you into the sun-soaked formal living and dining rooms, complete with wainscoting and a bay window. The spacious vaulted ceiling family room includes a cozy fireplace with a view of the landscaped backyard. The impressive eat-in kitchen features stained cabinets, granite countertops, an island w/breakfast bar, and stainless kitchen appliances.  The main-level primary suite is a true retreat with dual walk-in closets and a spa-style ensuite boasting dual vanities, a soaking tub, and a separate shower. Upstairs, you will find four secondary bedrooms and two full bathrooms. Enjoy outdoor relaxation and entertainment on the oversized patio and gazebo area with a walkout fenced backyard. Just minutes from shopping, dining, Hartsfield Jackson International Airport, and with easy highway access, this is the ultimate luxury living experience you've been waiting for!
